OL,3,CRural communities 'very vulnerable' as
OL,4,Coil prices double amid war in Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FPeople in rural parts of the region
OL,8,Fwho rely on oil to heat their homes
OL,9,Fsay they feel "very vulnerable" as
OL,10,Fprices have more than doubled since
OL,11,Fthe start of the war in Middle East.
OL,13,FThe average cost of kerosene has risen
OL,14,Fsharply to more than 140p per litre,
OL,15,Fand many oil companies have stopped
OL,16,Fdelivering due to high demand.
OL,18,FThe Government says it is exploring
OL,19,Fways to help - but residents whose
OL,20,Fbills are soaring say it must come
OL,21,Fsoon.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
