CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773234702
OL,3,CRural communities 'very vulnerable' as
OL,4,Coil prices double amid war in Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FCarole Miller, from Gweek in Cornwall,
OL,8,Frelies on oil deliveries for heating
OL,9,Fand hot water. Her husband is disabled
OL,10,Fso she says she cannot afford to run
OL,11,Fout.
OL,13,F"We bought some oil about six weeks
OL,14,Fago, we've just ordered again, and it
OL,15,Fhas actually doubled," she said.
OL,17,F"It's quite a shock really, and it's
OL,18,Freally worrying how things are going.
OL,19,FIt's going to be a worry for everyone."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
