OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773234702
OL,3,CRural communities 'very vulnerable' as
OL,4,Coil prices double amid war in Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FThe conflict in the Middle East is
OL,8,Fhaving an impact across the UK. The
OL,9,Fheating oil sector is particularly
OL,10,Fvolatile as it's unregulated, leaving
OL,11,Fpeople in rural communities feeling
OL,12,Funcertain about what the future holds.
OL,14,FCarole explained: "We do feel very
OL,15,Fvulnerable, my husband is quite
OL,16,Fdisabled so we have to keep the
OL,17,Fheating on and plenty of hot water.
OL,18,FAnd this is just the start of it, we
OL,19,Fjust don't know what's going to
OL,20,Fhappen."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773234702
OL,3,CRural communities 'very vulnerable' as
OL,4,Coil prices double amid war in Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FThe average cost of a litre of
OL,8,Fkerosene has risen sharply - from
OL,9,Faround 60p per litre at the start of
OL,10,Fthe year, to today's price of more
OL,11,Fthan 140p per litre. This means a
OL,12,Fdelivery of 500 litres is costing
OL,13,Fhouseholds more than #700 a go.
OL,15,FMatt Copeland, from National Energy
OL,16,FAction, said: "People using heating
OL,17,Foil get hit by it much quicker because
OL,18,Fof the lack of a price cap.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773234702
OL,3,CRural communities 'very vulnerable' as
OL,4,Coil prices double amid war in Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,F"If this lasts for months instead of
OL,8,Fweeks, it could have a really
OL,9,Fprolonged impact and much higher
OL,10,Fprices where people are forced to pay
OL,11,Fthrough the roof to fill up their
OL,12,Fheating oil tanks.
OL,14,F"What the Government can do is help
OL,15,Fpeople here. So if this is prolonged,
OL,16,Fthe Government will need to provide
OL,17,Fsupport to people."
OL,19,FAnalysis from ITV West Country's
OL,20,FPolitical Correspondent Alicia
OL,21,FFitzgerald
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
