OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773234702
OL,3,CRural communities 'very vulnerable' as
OL,4,Coil prices double amid war in Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FGovernments cannot control the global
OL,8,Foil price directly, but they can
OL,9,Freduce its impact on households and
OL,10,Fbusinesses.
OL,12,FOne immediate way they could do this
OL,13,Fis through subsidisation of energy
OL,14,Fbills, or offering grants to low
OL,15,Fincome households.
OL,17,FThis approach was used during previous
OL,18,Fenergy crises, but would be seen as a
OL,19,Flast resort owing to tight government
OL,20,Fbudgets.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773234702
OL,3,CRural communities 'very vulnerable' as
OL,4,Coil prices double amid war in Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FAnother quick way would be to reduce
OL,8,Fthe rate of fuel duty (currently due
OL,9,Fto increase this autumn), which is a
OL,10,Fmajor contributor to the price you see
OL,11,Fat the petrol pumps.
OL,13,FLonger term, reducing reliance on
OL,14,Fvolatile overseas oil - whether that
OL,15,Fbe by investing in home-grown
OL,16,Frenewable energy or expanding North
OL,17,FSea Oil production will make the UK
OL,18,Fmore resilient in the wake of a global
OL,19,Fshockwave.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773234702
OL,3,CRural communities 'very vulnerable' as
OL,4,Coil prices double amid war in Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FChancellor Rachel Reeves has told MPs
OL,8,Fthat the Government is exploring
OL,9,Foptions.
OL,11,FShe said: "I recognise that households
OL,12,Fwho use heating oil face unique
OL,13,Fchallenges, and so I have asked the
OL,14,FFinancial Secretary to the Treasury to
OL,15,Flead discussions with officials and
OL,16,Fwith rural and Northern Irish MPs to
OL,17,Fexplore further action that we can
OL,18,Ftake."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
